{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/GAMEPLAY.png?t=1689631780\" /><br>KAPITAL PUNISHMENT 22XX is a beat-em up, action platformer that features fast-paced, bloody combat with a retro aesthetic. Ruthless enemies hunt you through gritty prisons, hopeless company towns, and opulent sky-cities as you assemble a team of comrades to take down KAPITAL.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/ComradeAction.gif?t=1689631780\" /><br><br>Get ready to bash some fash!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/StoryMode.png?t=1689631780\" /><br>In the year 22XX, HOPE IS DEAD. A vile conglomerate of oligarchs lord over the fractured territories of the Americas from a floating fortress-city known as KAPITAL. This de facto cartel-state maintains control over the populace with brutal cyborg thugs known as KAPITAL OPERATIVES (KOPs).<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/EnemiesShowcase.gif?t=1689631780\" /><br><br>In Story Mode the game\u2019s narrative unfolds as you traverse through hand-crafted levels packed with platforming action. You\u2019ll battle bosses, make friends and enemies, and discover the grim truths of the 23rd century.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/MammonBossGif.gif?t=1689631780\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/ArcadeMode.png?t=1689631780\" /><br>In the Roguelike ARCADE MODE you\u2019ll battle hordes of foes in randomized arenas and compete on global leaderboards. Climb fences, mantle ledges, hang from bars, and leap from walls as you outmaneuver KOPs in search of upgrades and allies.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/MapsPermutation.gif?t=1689631780\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217680/extras/KEY_FEATURES.png?t=1689631780\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>AI-controlled comrades with unique abilities.<br></li><li>Relentless enemies that jump, climb, and fly to hunt you down.<br></li><li>Loads of power-ups to customize your build.<br></li><li>Engaging NPCs, dialog and platforming in STORY MODE.<br></li><li>White-knuckle action in the procedural generated arenas of ARCADE MODE.<br></li><li>Global Leaderboards.<br></li><li>Rogue-lite style unlocks tied to achievements.<br></li><li>Authentic 8-bit music to bash fash to.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Cells","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2217680/a6ea293a5c693da12f38082c558bc82d7b8b0fc7.jpg"},{"name":"The Labs","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2217680/ec1273d5b14f977b87935d4fe3b842ee82e4de48.jpg"},{"name":"The Prison Yard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2217680/7486b18a48e3c484d731ff895633b78af3d42ed7.jpg"},{"name":"Titus Englewood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2217680/65122906a71c1fa334e646436d9ae34aa0d35974.jpg"},{"name":"Vilma Rivera","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2217680/7ebc0c26be134447c6187954577b6ebfead451ca.jpg"},{"name":"Shakeel Foster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2217680/66d1b2757b4f9087da82223664b28ee96ac4f9e9.jpg"},{"name":"Brother","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2217680/d68e6609dcc8adde38b411c9d61854d30996ca5b.jpg"},{"name":"Heavy Arms","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pub